             Win a weekend break in Santorini
            </a>
            <div class="primary-large-card-description">
             Santorini is an island in the southern Aegean Sea, about 120 miles southeast of mainland Greece. MyOffers is giving away a holiday for two to this gorgeous destination which was voted as one of the world's most beautiful islands in 2015 by Travellers Choice Awards.
 Santorini has a small but flourishing wine industry producing both delicious red and white wines. You could combine winery tours with visiting local restaurants that always sell amazing sea food and traditional Greek dishes.
 Start your holiday by exploring Fira, the capital of Santorini. A city of white washed houses built on the edge of the 400 metres high caldera on the western edge of the island. Bus service runs from the city to most parts of the island. Take a day trip to the town of Thera where you can enjoy the breathtaking views whilst sitting in a cable car on your way down to the port. Plenty to choose from if you would like to scuba dive as there is nearly forty recognised scuba sites. Sea excursions can be experienced on a catamaran, a sailing boat or a traditional schooner. Or just admire the gorgeous volcanic black sand beaches of Santorini whilst sipping a local sangria.
 Put on a pair of comfortable shoes and visit the ancient city of Akrotiti, the most important archaeological site on the island dated back to 17th century BC. Nearby you will also find both, prehistoric, as well as archaeological museums of Thera.
 Do not forget to enter for a beautiful Spring break to Santorini before 31st July 2018 when MyOffers will be giving away a trip for two, flights and accommodations included.
            </div>

                                         <a href="https://twitter.com/home?status={{link}}" class="feed-card-properties-link" target="_blank" data-ga-tracking='{"eventCategory":"Home", "eventAction":"Social FTwitter Post Property", "eventLabel":"Favourite"}'>
                                             <span class="ico-font feed-card-properties-icon" title="favorite">&#xf004;</span>
                                             <span class="feed-card-properties-count">{{favorite}}</span>
                                         </a>
                                     </div>
                                     {{/favorite}}
                                 </div>
                             </div>
                         </div>
                     </div>
                     {{/twitter}}
                     {{#blog}}
                     <div class="feed-card-item">
                         <div class="feed-card-container" id="{{id}}">
                             {{#picture}}
                             <div class="feed-card-image-container">
                                 <a href="{{link}}" class="feed-card-image-link" target="_blank" data-ga-tracking='{"eventCategory":"Home", "eventAction":"Social Blog Post", "eventLabel":"Post Image"}'><img src="data:image/png;base64," data-src="{{picture}}" alt="{{media_type}}" class="feed-card-image lazyload card-start" width="{{picture_width}}" height="{{picture_height}}" /></a>
                             </div>
                             {{/picture}}
                             <div class="feed-card-header-container">
                                 <div class="feed-card-page-logo-container">
                                     <a href="{{link}}" class="feed-card-page-logo-link" target="_blank" data-ga-tracking='{"eventCategory":"Home", "eventAction":"Social Blog Post", "eventLabel":"Site Logo"}'><img src="{{social_icon}}" alt="{{social_name}}" class="feed-card-page-logo"></a>
                                 </div>
                                 <div class="feed-card-page-title-container">
                                     <strong class="feed-card-page-title {{social_type}}">{{social_name}}</strong>
                                     <span class="feed-card-page-subheading">{{display_date}}</span>
                                 </div>
                                 <div class="feed-card-logo-container">
                                     <a href="{{link}}" class="feed-card-logo-link" target="_blank"><i class="ico-font feed-card-logo {{social_type}}" data-ga-tracking='{"eventCategory":"Home", "eventAction":"Social Blog Post", "eventLabel":"Feed Logo"}'>&#xf09e;</i></a>
                                 </div>
                             </div> 
                             <div class="feed-card-description-container">
                                 <div class="feed-card-description {{social_type}}">
                                     <div class="social-content-heading">{{title}}</div>
                                     {{#message}}
                                     {{{message}}}
                                     {{/message}}
                                     <a href="{{link}}" class="social-content-link" data-ga-tracking='{"eventCategory":"Home", "eventAction":"Social Blog Post", "eventLabel":"Read the full post here"}'>Read the full post here</a>
                                 </div>
                             </div>
                             <div class="feed-card-properties-wrapper">
                                 <div class="feed-card-properties-container">
                                     <div class="feed-card-properties-item blog-properties-item">
                                         <a href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u={{link}}" class="feed-card-properties-link" target="_blank" data-ga-tracking='{"eventCategory":"Home", "eventAction":"Social Blog Post Property", "eventLabel":"Facebook"}'>
                                             <span class="ico-font feed-card-properties-icon" title="Share on Facebook">&#xf09a;</span>
                                         </a>
                                     </div>
                                     <div class="feed-card-properties-item blog-properties-item">
                                         <a href="http://twitter.com/share?text={{title}}&url={{link}}" class="feed-card-properties-link" target="_blank" data-ga-tracking='{"eventCategory":"Home", "eventAction":"Social Blog Post Property", "eventLabel":"Twitter"}'>
                                             <span class="ico-font feed-card-properties-icon" title="Share on Twitter">&#xf099;</span>
                                         </a>
                                     </div>
                                     <div class="feed-card-properties-item blog-properties-item">
                                         <a href="https://pinterest.com/pin/create/button/?url={{link}}&media={{picture}}&description={{title}}" class="feed-card-properties-link" target="_blank" data-ga-tracking='{"eventCategory":"Home", "eventAction":"Social Pinterest Post Property", "eventLabel":"Pinterest"}'>
                                             <span class="ico-font feed-card-properties-icon" title="Share on Pinterest">&#xe917;</span>
                                         </a>
                                     </div>
                                 </div>
                             </div>
                         </div>
                     </div>
                     {{/blog}}
                 {{/.}}
        </script>
       </section>
